channel.title: ▓▒░Demise's Open Client. 100% Stances, 3D Hp Bars, Moving Water And PvP Armor░▒▓
channel.description:
IVE STOPPED DOING SERVER PROJECTS AND IM NOW DOING MY OWN SERVER!
I was currently making a client for the server massacred world, but due to some technical difficulties it couldnt connect (itll work fine on your server) so ive decided to release it to the moparscape public :)
[size=15pt][u][b]Please dont flame like leech amg this is easy and other bs like that. This is easier for the total noobs that have no idea how to code or people that simply get errors trying to do this kind of stuff. This is completely just to help people seeing as my server isnt even online anymore and ive worked really hard on doing this.. so 1 flame ill just delete it.. cba with un needed abuse[/b][/u][/size]
CREDS TO EVERYONE WHOS CODE THIS IS.. DONT BOTHER ME ABOUT IT
[size=20pt][u][b]-><-Features-><-[/b][/u][/size]
HD right click interface (like runescape)
When applied with the correct emotes (server sided) teles work exactly like rs.
Godsword stances when running, walking, blocking and standing
3D hp bars to replace those horrible red n green ones
Non excessively used customs, only customs included are the most popular, E.G death cape, donor cape, vesta, stat and all pvp armors.
Actual runescape background
When you click run the horrible server thing doesnt appear, just the java
